    <item>
      <title>多晶硅生产商称中国太阳能行业正处于“深度下行周期”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/gcl-tech-china-solar-firms-in-deep-down-cycle-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[协鑫科技控股副总裁宋艾米表示，许多中国太阳能制造商正面临严重的衰退。她表示，小企业裁员似乎是永久性的。她在《彭博：中国秀》节目中与大卫·英格尔斯和安娜贝尔·德鲁勒斯讨论了这个行业。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-14/gcl-tech-china-solar-firms-in-deep-down-cycle-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元下跌，债券期货上涨，因日本央行推迟公布债务购买细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行表示将减少债务购买量但将细节推迟到下次政策会议后，日元走弱，日本主权债券价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:34:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行推迟削减债券购买规模导致日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行要求投资者等到 7 月份会议后才能公布有关缩减债券购买规模的细节，这导致日元再度走软，并推迟了加息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
